##  How do you plan to make it interactive? (What features of ggplot2/shiny/markdown do you plan to use to make the story interactive)

To make it interactive I plan on creating a slider with shiny for one of my visualizations so that the user can filter on which championships they want to focus on.
I also want to create an interactive game in which the user clicks on a jump and they'll be able to see the details concerning it, like how many revolutions, a short description on what its and its base value within the scoring system.

